幾日內無食過嘅客人都可以照去，但今日食左嘅客，未來幾日就可以分散幫其他黃店<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得呢個idea 點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:34:19.000Z","msg":"所以去舖頭仔 .com <a href=\"https://poutauzai.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpoutauzai.com&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=13f82a97\" target=\"_blank\">https://poutauzai.com</a>撐下啲黃小店<br />\n個網仲develop緊"},{"pid":"94678d4d307ba2e043379f1921c78d4f39f12ae1","tid":1817550,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"546dec3e4de5e17753b13224020ab76d9e372578","tid":1817550,"uid":163533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:32:46.000Z","msg":"我姪仔幾歲人仔都要佢老豆老母帶佢食夠100間黃店<br />\n做唔到咪認自己係深黃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:35:14.000Z","msg":"好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b57145c41f6a8eedfa61e22c301e8f9914b7bbf","tid":1817550,"uid":70494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:35:43.000Z","msg":"輪住食<br />\n每星期7間"},{"pid":"2c5310cfaf29d2d7765eefc1b0423ea83fb3cd25","tid":1817550,"uid":233009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:37:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bc755883d76c5529b75cc4879d402c17ea5ea9c8","tid":1817550,"uid":4838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:37:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ca589c850988969a9ed68726e556b341c4e610d5","tid":1817550,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:38:45.000Z","msg":"我會去幫趁啲小店 唔可以淨係罰啲大店"},{"pid":"9676d6290d5ca5172c4fb6047c9f978fdc387cf4","tid":1817550,"uid":329698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"講左勁耐<br />\n啲人都係一日到黑去龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9278b2fc27cef5072707c282542ff02b28aac618","tid":1817550,"uid":77666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T10:45:53.000Z","msg":"岩啊 咁樣只會令部份黃店可以生存"},{"pid":"e3d6c9f